<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title, description }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-page text-text-primary font-body antialiased overflow-x-hidden">
  <canvas id="dot-grid" class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div id="cursor-glow" class="fixed w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 pt-20">
    <section class="py-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Free Resources</span>
        <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-black tracking-tight">Practical AI resources</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-text-primary">No fluff. No gatekeeping.</p>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Guides, frameworks, and tools to help you figure out what AI can actually do for your business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card overflow-hidden">
          <div class="grid gap-0 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">
            <div class="p-8 lg:p-12">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <span class="rounded-full bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Featured</span>
                <span class="rounded-full border border-border-subtle px-3 py-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-text-secondary">Guide + Walkthrough</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="mt-6 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Build Your Own AI Executive Assistant</h2>
              <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                A real walkthrough of how I built an AI assistant that handles inbox, calendar, and follow-up. Not a concept. An actual build you can learn from and adapt.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Full build walkthrough, step by step</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Patterns that apply to any service business</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>A concrete example of what good AI ops actually looks like in practice</span></li>
              </ul>
              <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="/ai-ea-signup" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Get the Guide</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-border-subtle lg:border-l lg:border-t-0 p-8 lg:p-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="mx-auto flex h-24 w-24 items-center justify-center rounded-3xl border border-accent/20 bg-page/60 text-accent">
                  <svg class="h-12 w-12" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-7 4h8M7 4h6l4 4v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H7a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-text-primary">AI Executive Assistant</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-text-muted">Practical resource</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-12 text-center">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Resource Library</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Where to go next</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
          <a href="/ai-audit" class="glass-card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/30" data-tilt>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Free Audit</p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold">AI Audit</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">A free 30-minute session to map your operations, find what's leaking, and figure out what's worth building first.</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium text-accent">See details</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/vision-map" class="glass-card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/30" data-tilt>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Strategy Offer</p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Vision Map</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">For teams past the "should we use AI" question and stuck on where to start. The Vision Map gives you the order.</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium text-accent">Explore the offer</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/ai-mastermind" class="glass-card p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/30" data-tilt>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Community</p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-display font-bold">AI Mastermind</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">A weekly call for people actually building with AI. Not a webinar. A real conversation.</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium text-accent">Join the conversation</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm lg:pb-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14 text-center">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Need Something Specific?</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Not sure where to start?</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            If you've done the reading and want to talk through what applies to your business, book a call. It's free and there's no obligation.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="https://calendly.com/cosminlungu/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Book a Call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/dot-grid.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/magnetic.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/tilt.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
